{{Infobox artist | name = Kaja Norum | image = | imagesize = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1989|4|17}} | birth_place = Lørenskog, Norway | death_date = | death_place = | nationality = [[Norway|Norwegian]] | field = [[Painting]], [[Fashion model|modeling]] | training = | movement = | works = | patrons = | influenced = | awards = }}
'''Kaja Norum''' (born April 17, 1989) is a [[Norwegian people|Norwegian]] model and [[Figurative art|figurativist painter]].<ref>{{cite news|last=Treborg|first=Ingrid Marie|title=Slik ble norske Kaja elskerinnen til Tommy Lee|url=http://www.tv2.no/underholdning/gkn/slik-ble-norske-kaja-elskerinnen-til-tommy-lee-3303023.html|accessdate=3 January 2013|newspaper=tv2.no|date=1 October 2010|language=Norwegian}}</ref> A former student and protégé of painter [[Odd Nerdrum]],<ref name=a>{{cite news|last=Nyfløt|first=Hilda|title=- Jeg stilte opp fordi det er morsomt å posere|url=http://www.dagbladet.no/2011/10/16/nyheter/det_nye/kaja_norum/aylar_lie/caroline_berg_eriksen/18607784/|accessdate=3 January 2013|newspaper=Dagbladet.no|date=16 October 2011|language=Norwegian}}</ref> Norum is devoted to Nerdrum's philosophy of [[The Kitsch Movement|Kitsch painting]], and is a part of The Kitsch Movement spawned by Nerdrum. After the latter relocated to [[France]] in 2011, Norum is the primary caretaker of his gallery and his estate.<ref>{{cite news|last=Hegseth|first=Morten|title=Nerdrums stjerneelev flytter in på kunstgården|url=http://pluss.vg.no/2011/08/16/514/514_20089109|accessdate=3 January 2013|newspaper=vg.no|date=16 August 2011|language=Norwegian}}</ref>
==Early life and education== Born in [[Lørenskog]], [[Akershus]]. Norum attended the [[Rudolf Steiner School in Lørenskog]] graduating in 2005, after which she enrolled at the Oslo City Steiner School. After graduating from high school in 2008, Norum relocated to [[Stavern]] in order to study under kitsch painter Odd Nerdrum at his seaside gallery.<ref>{{cite news|last=Olsen|first=Elisabeth|title=I Nerdrums fotspor|url=http://www.rb.no/lokal_kultur/article5060219.ece|accessdate=3 January 2013|newspaper=Romerikes blad|date=7 April 2010|language=Norwegian}}</ref>
==Career==
===Painting=== After studying under Nerdrum in Stavern for three years, Norum debuted with her own exhibition in June 2011. The exhibition, which consisted of figurative artworks turned out to be a success with the majority of the artworks being sold on the opening day. It attracted large attention with the most famous painting depicting comedian [[Sturla Berg-Johansen]] with an [[Phallus|erect penis]].<ref>{{cite news|last=Kristiansen|first=Sandra Marie|title=Sturla Berg Johansen pryder maleri med erigert penis|url=http://www.tv2.no/underholdning/gkn/sturla-berg-johansen-pryder-maleri-med-erigert-penis-3528670.html|accessdate=3 January 2013|newspaper=tv2.no|date=26 June 2011|language=Norwegian}}</ref> The painting, ''"Homo ludens"'' valued at US$14.500, was sold to an anonymous buyer.<ref>{{cite news|last=Treborg|first=Ingrid Marie|title=Kaja Norum overrasket med penismaleri: – Sturla-bildet var selvfølgelig planlagt|url=http://www.tv2.no/underholdning/gkn/kaja-norum-overrasket-med-penismaleri-sturlabildet-var-selvfoelgelig-planlagt-3569914.html|accessdate=3 January 2013|newspaper=tv2.no|date=28 August 2011|language=Norwegian}}</ref> It was speculated that the buyer was either hotel tycoon [[Petter Stordalen]] or business magnate [[Stein Erik Hagen]],<ref>{{cite news|last=Lunde|first=Mikael|title=Vil ikke ha Sturlas penis på veggen|url=http://www.dagbladet.no/2011/06/29/kultur/odd_nerdrum/kaja_norum/kunst/sturla_berg-johansen/17114999/|accessdate=3 January 2013|newspaper=Dagbladet.no|date=29 June 2011|language=Norwegian}}</ref> however it was later revealed that it was actually a gourmet restaurant in [[Oslo]] that had made the purchase.<ref>{{cite news|last=Lunder|first=Martine|title=Humordronning kjøpte omstridt bilde: - Alle skal få se naken-Sturla|url=http://www.vg.no/rampelys/artikkel.php?artid=10096569|accessdate=3 January 2013|newspaper=vg.no|date=5 July 2011|language=Norwegian}}</ref> In August 2012 Norum opened her second exhibition, at the Gallery Soon in [[Son]] in [[Vestby]].<ref>{{cite news|last=Andersen|first=Christina|title=– Jeg er ikke særlig sjenert I dag åpner Kaja Norum en ny utstilling på Galleri Soon.|url=http://www.moss-avis.no/kultur/jeg-er-ikke-serlig-sjenert-1.7470455|accessdate=3 January 2013|newspaper=Moss avis|date=4 August 2012|language=Norwegian}}</ref>
===Modeling=== Norum has done modeling for the magazines '' [[Det Nye]]'' and ''[[Alfa (magazine)|Alfa]]''.<ref name=a/> In January 2013 she appeared in the magazine ''Kamille'' doing nude photos.<ref>{{cite news|last=Bjørnstad|first=Guro|title=- Odd Nerdrum snakket alltid om at det skulle være "kjøttfullt"|url=http://www.kjendis.no/2013/01/02/kjendis/kaja_norum/kunst/odd_nerdrum/kropp/25051491/|accessdate=3 January 2013|newspaper=Dagbladet.no|date=2 January 2013|language=Norwegian}}</ref>
